metadata.name: Candidate #0001
metadata.description: The Cannibals is a collection that permits holders access to Project Divinity's 'Crypto Island' experiment. Project Divinity is a secret organization set on rebuilding the world in a fair, just manner. The 'Crypto Island' experiment is just one of many ways Project Divinity is determining who will be allowed to join their organization in the new world order. Do you have what it takes to get off of 'Crypto Island'? Project Divinity is rewarding those that are worthy.
